Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Iran hostage crisis goes on
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w1n6
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 2 Mar 1980
Iran refuses negotiation attempt over US hostages the country is holding. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.